#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This tool allows you to set the color scheme for the current Plasma session, "
"without accidentally setting it to one that is either not available, or "
"which is already set."
msgstr ""
"このツールで、誤って利用不可能なものもしくは既に設定されているものを設定する"
"ことなく、現在の Plasma セッションのカラースキームを設定できます。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The name of the color scheme you wish to set for your current Plasma session "
"(passing a full path will only use the last part of the path)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:48
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show all the color schemes available on the system (and which is the current "
"theme)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:53
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The name of the accent color you want to set. SVG color names (https://"
"www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/types.html#ColorKeywords) and hex color codes are "
"supported. Quote the hex code if there is possibility of shell expansion"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:80
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The requested theme \"%1\" is already set as the theme for the current "
"Plasma session."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:113
#, kde-format
msgid "Successfully applied the color scheme %1 to your current Plasma session"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:115
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Could not find theme \"%1\". The theme should be one of the following "
"options: %2"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have managed to pass an empty color scheme name, which isn't supported "
"behavior."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:127
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The file you attempted to set as your scheme, %1, could not be identified as "
"a color scheme."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:151
#, kde-format
msgid "Successfully applied the accent color %1"
msgstr "アクセントカラー %1 の適用に成功しました"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: plasma-apply-colorscheme.cpp:153
#, kde-format
msgid "Invalid accent color "
msgstr "無効なアクセントカラー"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
